  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EAT AND GROW!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425390/extras/4cb2fa6555e0307068eeb221ba5b2956.poster.avif?t=1737209686\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425390/extras/4cb2fa6555e0307068eeb221ba5b2956.webm?t=1737209686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425390/extras/4cb2fa6555e0307068eeb221ba5b2956.mp4?t=1737209686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eat smaller fish to grow bigger and become the king of the ocean!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategically grow to hunt larger fish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>6 Unique Maps</strong>: Each filled with its own challenges and enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Mode</strong>: Test yourself and reach the highest score. Only the fastest and most attentive can survive!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EARN AND COLLECT REWARDS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every 3 stars you earn gives you 10 in-game currency (TBP). Use it to unlock more customization options and develop your aquarium.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MANAGE YOUR AQUARIUM</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425390/extras/ef2da0ebea15712117320b10ac42416d.poster.avif?t=1737209686\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425390/extras/ef2da0ebea15712117320b10ac42416d.webm?t=1737209686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425390/extras/ef2da0ebea15712117320b10ac42416d.mp4?t=1737209686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Feed and Grow Your Own Fish</strong>: In Aquarium Mode, you can feed, grow, and even sell your fish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Feed Management</strong>: Keep your fish healthy by using various types of food.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Oxygen and Cleanliness Levels</strong>: Always keep your aquarium clean and maintain high oxygen levels to keep your fish happy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>External Threats</strong>: Your aquarium can be attacked. Raise defense fish and protect it from enemies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eat or DIE!</strong> is the perfect game for those seeking both excitement and a relaxing experience. Start your underwater adventure today and become the king of the ocean!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EAT AND GROW!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425390/extras/4cb2fa6555e0307068eeb221ba5b2956.poster.avif?t=1737209686\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425390/extras/4cb2fa6555e0307068eeb221ba5b2956.webm?t=1737209686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425390/extras/4cb2fa6555e0307068eeb221ba5b2956.mp4?t=1737209686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eat smaller fish to grow bigger and become the king of the ocean!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategically grow to hunt larger fish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>6 Unique Maps</strong>: Each filled with its own challenges and enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Mode</strong>: Test yourself and reach the highest score. Only the fastest and most attentive can survive!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EARN AND COLLECT REWARDS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every 3 stars you earn gives you 10 in-game currency (TBP). Use it to unlock more customization options and develop your aquarium.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MANAGE YOUR AQUARIUM</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425390/extras/ef2da0ebea15712117320b10ac42416d.poster.avif?t=1737209686\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425390/extras/ef2da0ebea15712117320b10ac42416d.webm?t=1737209686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425390/extras/ef2da0ebea15712117320b10ac42416d.mp4?t=1737209686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Feed and Grow Your Own Fish</strong>: In Aquarium Mode, you can feed, grow, and even sell your fish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Feed Management</strong>: Keep your fish healthy by using various types of food.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Oxygen and Cleanliness Levels</strong>: Always keep your aquarium clean and maintain high oxygen levels to keep your fish happy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>External Threats</strong>: Your aquarium can be attacked. Raise defense fish and protect it from enemies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eat or DIE!</strong> is the perfect game for those seeking both excitement and a relaxing experience. Start your underwater adventure today and become the king of the ocean!</p>",
